<span class="hl_good"><span class="hl_keyword">lemma</span> detect_sound:<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;all-traces<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class="hl_operator">∀ </span>ki kr #t1<span class="hl_operator">.</span><br/>
